Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請你多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  看了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  里中
