Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映在午夜電視上的女孩子究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇  你的字好醜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為雪子記了筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原  原來如此…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多保重
