Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  給人添麻煩也要適可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們如果不是堂島先生的外甥和他的朋友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可就不是警告一下就能了事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  里中？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天城？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說她直到昨天傍晚為止都還在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之後誰都沒有再看到過雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實天城雪子的家人已經提交了尋人申請
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是雪子小姐的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你們有想到什麼線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說雪子小姐看起來很痛苦之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很痛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的受害人山野女主播  案發前住在天城屋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是投訴似乎蜂擁而至
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果老闆娘因為壓力過大而倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後雪子小姐正好是老闆娘的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局裡也有人說她因為有著見不得人的理由而躲起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思啊  你想說雪子是犯人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  這終究只是謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子怎麼可能是犯人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷靜點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這謠言又不是我傳出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  里中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  雪子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須去救雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天午夜電視裡出現的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中你最好還是在外面等我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去  我絕對要去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要一說出口  就再也不聽勸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊  天城就在這裡面吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯熊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊的鼻子都能清楚地聞到呢熊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要一個人去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你沒辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下熊熊啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙  完全沒有在意周圍的情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是老師啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽介還需要繼續努力啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我就直呼其名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…雪子的房間？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼「紅色真適合你呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很討厭雪子這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪什麼的  冰冷且轉眼間就會消融
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是虛無縹緲的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}但是  卻和我非常相稱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子…你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}和除了繼承旅館之外毫無價值的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡啊  回答我啊  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  只有千枝這麼對我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  紅色真適合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有千枝給予了我生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千枝既開朗又堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且什麼都會做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所沒有的東西  她全都擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種  我這種人和千枝比起來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千枝會保護我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善解人意的千枝會保護這個毫無價值的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善解人意的千枝什麼的  真是笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？  是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是里中千枝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你在說什麼啊  我才是里中千枝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是里中千枝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事  真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  那個雪子居然說她被我保護著？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說自己毫無價值  不這樣怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子是個美女  皮膚又白  還很有女人味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都被男生們捧在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的雪子時不時會用自卑的眼神看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺真是讓人爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子其實是個離開了我就什麼都做不到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的地位  我的地位顯然要比她高得多不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  里中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  不對  這根本不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼數量啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一樣  裝作沒看見不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快來鎮住我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口  你這種傢伙  你這種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種傢伙才不是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾即為影  是為真實的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  你也要來礙事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓你吃點苦頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  你太帥了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還存在著啊？  快點給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我會負責照顧雪子的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為墊腳石來照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墊腳…石？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人的話就什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我才是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經無可救藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但雪子卻依靠著這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以雪子是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里…中  不要被迷惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:17:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼迷惑不迷惑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我的真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心…話！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子是個美女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被男人們追捧著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這就是你內心深處的真實想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醜陋的嫉妒之心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明離開了我就什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是全都在依賴著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是  我的  真心話？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心話？  這不也挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  你們也是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子…  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  我們是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我內心深處的另一個我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我一直都不敢面對的  無可救藥的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我就是我  對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你想認同並接受我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我就這樣把你撕成碎片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽陽陽陽介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從羈絆中獲得了新的Arcana
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠使用多個Persona的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「Wild」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——被選中之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被選中…之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Change
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs17\pos(320,327)}Jack O'Lantern
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑克南瓜燈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太  太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙  能使用兩種Persona嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.97,0:21:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看起來很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明如果這邊下起霧的話  雪子說不定會死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的身體卻不聽使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拯救天城的話  里中的力量一定是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為謝禮  我就破例讓你看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它被養在我家裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長的胖乎乎的  而且還非常臭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  正是這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我邂逅了我最好的朋友雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:08.43,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c000000}人之間的羈絆就是真正的力量
Comment: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
