Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.53,0:24:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千枝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.62,0:24:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擋路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.95,0:24:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.12,0:24:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.12,0:24:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那個時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.12,0:24:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會逃避的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.90,0:24:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠了那種煩人的束縛了
